%C	- Display a splash screen including uname and network interface information.

Display an image as a background with forground text listing interface MAC/IP addresses,
uname information and some hints for accessing this instance of QNX.

%C [-d device] [-D dispno] [-l layer_index] [-f font_file] file

-d device	Index of GF device to attach to, in the order that they are
                encountered in /dev/io-display. Default is the first device.
-D dispno       Index of the display to attach to. Default is (first display).
-l layer_index	Index of layer to render to.  Default is the main display layer.
-f font_file	Font file for text output.  Default is tt0419m_.ttf (Courier10).
file		The name of the image file to load.		
